name: Inter-Space Operation: Journey to the Earth
name_original: Inter-Space Operation: Journey to the Earth
description:
Travel the terrestrial planets, on a mission from Mars to Earth herself. There are many challenges that lay before you, both physical and mental. Are you up to the task? 

This game runs on Unity 2021.3.1f1 and runs natively on Windows. This game is very lightweight, so it should work on virtually any Windows computer. 

Music by Marcel Harrison: https://www.reverbnation.com/marcel9 

Rocket boost sound effect by impe93: Rocket Sound
